{"id": 1036, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法忍受哪种客户？", "description": "又想乙方跑，又想乙方不吃草（围笑）。（题目来自：John Holcroft）", "record_count": 2469, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130136rDauTQcGRnJ7AHfi.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-27T11:00:32Z", "options": [{"id": 93441, "content": "想给你们公司改改规章制度", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632190}, {"id": 93443, "content": "事兒逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483563}, {"id": 93444, "content": "性急 催命", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483563}, {"id": 93700, "content": "给客户改方案千百遍，他还嫌你不用心。。咱的构造又不是机器人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652090}, {"id": 93445, "content": "自以为是，从不满足", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648274}, {"id": 93701, "content": "不行，改\n还是不好，再改\n我家狗狗不喜欢，继续改", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38139}, {"id": 93447, "content": "“等我打电话问一个专业朋友”你特么倒是直接找他去啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659369}, {"id": 93448, "content": "难道我的中国风演绎得相当完美？赞美是我前进的动力！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528988}, {"id": 94985, "content": "讨价还价也得有礼貌！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653303}, {"id": 93450, "content": "“字大一点再大一点，图大一点再大一点！什么，这样不好看？排好看还不是你们美工的事么？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659393}, {"id": 104202, "content": "事儿多银子少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 93451, "content": "想让乙方把什么都做好了再出钱，说是了解行业，话说真正了解行业还要不出钱就先要设计的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118741}, {"id": 93452, "content": "很容易的，你聽我說.......", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658042}, {"id": 93453, "content": "什么都不懂还假装高大上", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659403}, {"id": 93454, "content": "斤斤计较，吹毛求疵的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659396}, {"id": 93455, "content": "如果我有想法，还找你们干嘛？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659412}, {"id": 93456, "content": "我觉得应该懂啊~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659412}, {"id": 93457, "content": "哦，还是用第一版吧~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659412}, {"id": 93458, "content": "不给钱还催着你干活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563637}, {"id": 93459, "content": "什么都不确定，来回的修改再修改，一直用预算吊着", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647018}, {"id": 93460, "content": "要高大上", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 93462, "content": "全世界都得围着他转呐", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659511}, {"id": 93464, "content": "美女客户", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 67471}, {"id": 93465, "content": "客户领导", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656256}, {"id": 93977, "content": "目中无人 不懂尊重  夜郎自大 肤浅无知", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662001}, {"id": 93467, "content": "这样子的☔️天适当?，并且心安理得。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183006SEcTlyYvGBdxgiqW.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528988}, {"id": 93468, "content": "这样子的☔️，适合?，并且心安理得。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183006DUhJcmrXIESFy4iu.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528988}, {"id": 93469, "content": "这样子的☔️，适合?，❤️安理得。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183006TFeYxIukPKOzHpti.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528988}, {"id": 93471, "content": "永远不满意然后拿你的设计稍一改就用了，永远不用付钱?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651208}, {"id": 93472, "content": "明知不合规矩还要让你做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576673}, {"id": 93473, "content": "磨磨唧唧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653999}, {"id": 93475, "content": "中标后告诉隐藏条款", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597421}, {"id": 93476, "content": "小米这种，产品技术不过关导致用户体验差，又经常说的自己很有创新一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443268}, {"id": 93477, "content": "心比天高，命比纸薄。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495259}, {"id": 93480, "content": "去餐厅吃饭 ，拿着餐牌却聊电话……挂电话看着餐牌很久……很久", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637065}, {"id": 93481, "content": "什么都不懂，还一直大吼大叫的? ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659729}, {"id": 93484, "content": "完全听不懂他要表达什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609292}, {"id": 93486, "content": "5点30分下单，今晚就要定", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659801}, {"id": 93494, "content": "给你许了一个又一个承诺说，有项目一定找你。因为这，就让你帮他做了一件又一件免费的他自己的事情，最后，项目和钱两空。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659805}, {"id": 97590, "content": "接头前总是让我多注意有人跟过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677431}, {"id": 84028, "content": "给钱不利索的，越穷事儿越多", "image": null, "praise_count": 510, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84029, "content": "要情怀、要高大上，但却没有明确诉求的", "image": null, "praise_count": 347, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84030, "content": "有着和年龄不相符合的天真烂漫。见过想让在校生自创剧本找陈可辛拍的客户吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84031, "content": "骗稿的", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 93770, "content": "20块钱的东西用了三年坏了，找过来要换个新的。zz", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661006}, {"id": 94796, "content": "死不做决定又一时一个想法的领导", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664376}, {"id": 93783, "content": "只给你一毛，却想要一万的那种效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146355}, {"id": 93811, "content": "不懂 还瞎bb", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201907}, {"id": 101500, "content": "装B了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687277}, {"id": 95617, "content": "问得比谁都详细一副“天呐  老子有钱又牛逼”  的模样  促成的时候又哭穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667875}]}